    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm just wondering why certain groups think it should be in schools at all? like, i hear some people say it's basically a requirement for being a good, modern parent, but then others say it's actually harmful. is there a consensus on which approach is actually better for kids' development?",
